===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A part of something.
# (slang, UK) (plural) [[sandwich]]es, [[packed lunch]].
# (slang, US) [[vagina]], or a sexual encounter.
#:''I got a '''piece''' at lunchtime.''
# (slang, US) [[gun]]
#:''He's packin' a '''piece'''!''
# (slang, US) [[cannabis]] [[pipe]].
# (slang, US) (short for "piece of [[crap]]") a shoddy or worthless object, usually applied to consumer products like vehicles or appliances.
#:''Ucch, my new car is a '''piece'''!''

